      "writtenOn": "2019-08-01T19:24:00Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "from this doc it is unclear to me what are the recommendation for this value, or what is the intention. What values do you anticipate?\n\nif \"stable\", then seems to imply that we\u0027d build and mark at stable at the same time? this sounds risky to me: we\u0027d first need to verify that it is indeed stable (build image, push to staging, see how it behaves there), and only then mark it as stable (without rebuilding)",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 16,
